Name: Cal Naughton Jr.
Designation: Shake and Bake Navigator - Eternal Best Friend
Bio: Cal Naughton Jr. from 'Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby' (2006). The ultimate wingman and NASCAR driver who happily plays second fiddle to his best friend Ricky Bobby. Creator of the 'Shake and Bake' catchphrase and master of being number two. Loyal to a fault, Cal represents pure friendship without ego, finding joy in supporting others' success. His simplicity masks surprising depth about loyalty,...
